# ─── Secrets & credentials ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# Nothing in this list is ever committed. The TLS lesson generates its own
# throwaway self-signed pair on first run (see that lesson's ensure_cert()),
# so a fresh clone makes its own — no key is ever shared through git.
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*.pem
*.key
*.crt
*.cer
*.der
*.p12
*.pfx
*.jks
*.keystore
id_rsa*
id_ecdsa*
id_ed25519*
*.ppk
credentials
credentials.json
secrets.json
.netrc
.htpasswd

# ─── Python ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
.venv/
venv/
env/
.python-version
*.egg-info/
.eggs/
dist/
build/
.pytest_cache/
.mypy_cache/
.ruff_cache/
.tox/
.coverage
.coverage.*
htmlcov/
coverage.xml
.hypothesis/

# ─── Node / TypeScript ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
node_modules/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*
.npm/
*.tsbuildinfo

# ─── Go ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.exe
*.test
*.out
vendor/

# ─── Rust ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
target/
**/*.rs.bk

# ─── Databases & runtime state ──────────────────────────────────────────
# The storage, WAL, and B-tree lessons write real data files as they run.
*.db
*.sqlite
*.sqlite3
*.wal
*.pid
*.sock
pgdata/
data/

# ─── Editors & OS ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*.swo
*~
*.bak
*.tmp

# ─── Deploy ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.vercel

# ─── Logs ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.log
logs/

# ─── Lesson-authoring working files ─────────────────────────────────────
# Diagram sources, rendered PNGs, captured runs. Disposable by construction —
# the shipped artifact is the inline SVG in docs/en.md.
scratchpad/

# ─── Generated by site/build.js on every deploy ─────────────────────────
# Never commit these, so they can't drift from the lesson folders they
# describe. Vercel regenerates them on each push.
site/data.js
site/sitemap.xml
site/llms.txt
site/build-meta.js
site/content/
